      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "The antenna summary should show you the affected net/pin.\nLibreLane allows you to manually insert antenna diodes:\n\n```\n...\n  substituting_steps:\n    +OpenROAD.DetailedRouting: Odb.InsertECODiodes\n...\n```\n\n```\nINSERT_ECO_DIODES:\n- target: instance/pin\n```",
